    java.io.Serializable

    public class Client
extends BaseModel<Client>
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class that models the Clients data and maps it's structure to the persistence layer, it also defines and implements the functions that can be performed with the Clients.

    According to our implementation a Client is an application that is allowed to call on the APIs
